data.description: 3 Bedroom home offers a variety of desirable features. Situated on a spacious lot, the property has a fenced yard, providing privacy for outdoor activities. The oversized 2 car garage not only offers ample space for parking but also includes a workshop area for DIY projects or storage. Additionally, there is an additional workshop located in the basement, providing even more space for your hobbies.One of the highlights of this home is the heated front porch, allowing you to enjoy the space comfortably throughout the year. perfect for a cozy reading nook or a spot to entertain guests. Step outside to the back patio, perfect for outdoor gatherings or simply relaxing. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer, a growing family, or someone seeking a cozy retreat, this three-bedroom home with its fenced yard, 2+ car garage, heated front porch, back patio with a privacy fence, vinyl siding, ample storage, and central air provides a range of amenities to suit your lifestyle needs.
